WEBVTT

00:02:55.666 --> 00:03:01.299
the Coalition for Epidemic
Preparedness Innovation, CEPI,

00:03:01.323 --> 00:03:04.555
was funded by our foundation,

00:03:04.579 --> 00:03:09.053
Wellcome Trust
and a number of governments,

00:03:09.077 --> 00:03:13.076
to do some of the platform vaccine work,

00:03:13.100 --> 00:03:18.584
but in the area of diagnostics,
antibodies, antivirals,

00:03:18.608 --> 00:03:21.467
basically doing the disease games
that I talked about,

00:03:21.491 --> 00:03:25.046
where we'd simulate
what needed to be done.

00:03:25.443 --> 00:03:27.025
We hardly did anything,

00:03:27.049 --> 00:03:31.356
and so now here we have
a respiratory virus